      "@danielmewes  @kamilion The bug is not in rethinkdb, the problem is in file permissions `(errno 13 - Permission denied)`. You should give execution permissions (711) to the whole path/directory `/mnt/btrfs/cloudmaster` with:\r\n\r\n```sh\r\nchmod 711 /mnt && chmod 711 /mnt/btrfs && chmod 711 /mnt/btrfs/cloudmaster\r\n```\r\n\r\n Now it's 700 so rethinkdb won't be able to access any file or subdirectory."
